TopicTitle: Cannot fold back the solar panel

Articles.Content:

Edited May 15, 2015 by cicatrix

prefix updated to solved
There are two types of solar panel of this size - with and without casing. To differentiate between the two, now only the one with the casing can be retracted after it is deployed.

Yeah, that's not a bug, it's intentional. The non-shrouded small panels are now no longer retractable. I think they did that to give you a reason to use the shrouded panels, other then just cosmetically. The toggle option still being in the action group tab is a bug,
I see, at least this could be reflected in the part's description.

Wow! I've been wondering what the deal is with my panels for a while.. jeez. The shrouded ones are heavier, yes? I guess that means they're going on the atmo landers!

Thanks!
